cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: The paper discusses the application of computer vision and artificial intelligence techniques in analyzing cricket events. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the use of a CNN-based classification method and Inception V3 suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of multimedia data in cricket analysis suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
